\paragraph{IE from Books.} 
Prior works by [bamman-etal-2019-annotated, stammbach-etal-2022-heroes, chang-etal-2023-speak] pursue LLM-supported IE about characters from fiction books. However, these methods focus on generating a single name from a single passage.